cgisysinfo 0.4.1
----------------

Bugfix release.
Memory: fixed memory count when cached/buffered memory isn't provided.
        e.g. OpenVZ containers.


cgisysinfo 0.4
--------------

Network: just shows active interfaces. interfaces sorted by name.
File systems: revert "follow symbolic links" change. file systems sorted by
              mount point.
Memory: added support to TB size for output.
Minor improvements


cgisysinfo 0.3
--------------

Code cleanup. Follow symbolic links for disk devices. Minor improvements.


cgisysinfo 0.2
--------------

Added optional FastCGI support.


cgisysinfo 0.1
--------------

First public release.

